{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0MzU5ODAwNjIw", "number": 1174, "title": "Fix display issues on exercise overview and detail pages", "bodyText": "I tested all changes and all related features with different users (student, tutor, instructor, admin) on the test server https://artemistest.ase.in.tum.de.\n Server: I added multiple integration tests (Spring) related to the features\n Server: I added @PreAuthorize and check the course groups for all new REST Calls (security)\n Server: I implemented the changes with a good performance and prevented too many database calls\n Server: I documented the Java code using JavaDoc style.\n Client: I added multiple integration tests (Jest) related to the features\n Client: I added authorities to all new routes and check the course groups for displaying navigation elements (links, buttons)\n Client: I documented the TypeScript code using JSDoc style.\n Client: I added multiple screenshots/screencasts of my UI changes\n Client: I translated all the newly inserted strings into German and English\n\nMotivation and Context\nFixes #1122.\nDescription\n\nFix overlap of tabs and filters on exercise overview (see screenshot 1.)\nCenter align icon with text on result progress bar (see screenshot 2.)\nEnsure that container of result string does not exceed viewport (see screenshot 3.1. and 3.2.)\n\nSteps for Testing\n\nLog in to Artemis\nNavigate to Overview\nClick on a course\nCheck the course overview page itself and click on individual exercises\n\nScreenshots\n\nFixed overlap of tabs (Exercises, Lectures, ...) and checkbox filter line:\n\n\n\n\nIcon alignment and full divider line:\n\n\n\n3.1. Result string is no longer cut off on small screens:\n\n\n3.2. Result string is no longer cut off on small screens:\n\n\n\nBug was mentioned in issue but has been resolved already by @krusche: Vertical space between complaint buttons and Q&A box:", "createdAt": "2020-01-07T02:56:28Z", "url": "https://github.com/ls1i